description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 27, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 81, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Nine Lives for East, 8 for South, and 3 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90273-49832-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [81 Votes, Common]
